column5: Be part of Pete's FIRST PODCAST! We would LOVE to hear from you!  Call in and leave a message on the podcast message line before May 16th with your questions, your fishing success stories, favorite fishing spots, tips etc.,  The number to call is (702) 995-2908.  Be sure to leave your name and location on the voicemail (i.e. this is Joe in Wausau, Wisconsin)  Then go to www.PeteMaina.com on May 23rd click and listen!  -Jen
Can you pick up the show on  SIRIUS SATELLITE RADIO . THAT would be nice to listen to while out fishing here in ontario canada.    MR PIKE.
